This paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories:

1. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new algorithm for deep reinforcement learning that is highly sample efficient. This falls under the domain of machine learning.

2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach for learning hierarchical skills in reinforcement learning. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence.

3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper uses raw pixel data to discover objects and learn skills. This falls under the domain of computer vision.

4. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper proposes an algorithm for learning skills that can control interactions with objects in the physical world. This falls under the domain of robotics.

5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes an algorithm for learning hierarchical skills that can control interactions with objects in the physical world. This falls under the domain of systems and control.
